    "body": "Adds a compile-time check that rejects parameters declared with `not None` that also have a default value of `None`, since the default can never be used without raising `TypeError` at runtime.\n\nFixes #7762",
    "closed_at": "2026-06-24T06:40:07Z",
    "comment_data": [],
    "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/cython/cython/issues/7764/comments",
